reviewText: Been a Stern fan for ages. I remember watching this when I was younger. I was happy to find the video tape. It is, however, rather raunchy at parts and I guess I'm just getting old and find it a little uncomfortable to watch with others. Still, though, glad I ordered it and got to watch again. The tape played very well. Held up good for an old VHS.
Don't think twice about this one... Howard and the crew in the early times. The making of pure genius... BaBaBooey...!!!

Classic Old School  Howard Stern! 3D Baba Booey effects.  You heard them talk about this pay per view special and VHS Tape on syndicated radio for twenty years. Gary, Stuttering John, Fred, Jessica Hahn, Howard and the Wack Pack. Good Deal for a old tape.
